headlines.description: McKenzie Milton threw for 346 yards and five touchdowns and No. 21 UCF routed UConn 56-17 on Thursday night to extend the longest winning streak in the nation to 14 games.
headlines.shortLinkText: No. 21 UCF extends winning streak to 14 with rout of UConn

events.name: New Mexico State Aggies at Minnesota Golden Gophers

headlines.description: True freshman walk-on Zack Annexstad threw two touchdown passes to Tyler Johnson in his debut, and Minnesota opened the season by overwhelming New Mexico State in a 48-10 victory on Thursday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Minnesota beats New Mexico St. 48-10 in QB Annexstad's debut

video.headline: Minnesota's Winfield goes Beast Mode for 76-yard punt return TD

events.name: Central Connecticut Blue Devils at Ball State Cardinals

headlines.description: Riley Neal threw for 259 yards and two touchdowns and Ball State amassed a school-record 652 offensive yards in a 42-6 win against Central Connecticut on Thursday night in the season opener for both teams.
headlines.shortLinkText: Ball St. offense explodes in 42-6 win against C. Connecticut

events.name: Kennesaw State Owls at Georgia State Panthers

headlines.description: Dan Ellington threw three touchdown passes, including an 8-yard score to Diondre Champaigne with 41 seconds left, to help Georgia State beat cross-town rival Kennesaw State 24-20 on Thursday night and avoid losing to an FCS school at home in...
headlines.shortLinkText: Georgia State scores late, edges Kennesaw State 24-20

events.name: Weber State Wildcats at Utah Utes

headlines.description: Zack Moss rushed for 150 yards and a touchdown and added a receiving score to power Utah to a 41-10 win over Weber State on Thursday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Moss Rushes for 150 yards; Utah rolls over Weber St., 41-10

video.headline: Moss takes it 86 yards to the house

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Moss takes it 86 yards to the house) 2018/08/30 ESHEET

events.name: Wake Forest Demon Deacons at Tulane Green Wave

headlines.description: Wake Forest freshman Sam Hartman passed for 378 yards and two touchdowns in his collegiate debut, Cade Carney powered in for a short TD in overtime, and the Demon Deacons defeated Tulane 23-17 on Thursday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Wake Forest survives to beat Tulane 23-17 in OT

headlines.description: Jeremy Larkin ran for a career-high 143 yards and scored two touchdowns in his first game as Northwestern's feature back and the Wildcats' sealed Thursday night's 31-27 victory at Purdue by running off the final 7 minutes, 57 seconds.
headlines.shortLinkText: Larkin helps Northwestern extend streak with win at Purdue

video.headline: Northwestern punches it in before halftime

events.name: Missouri State Bears at Oklahoma State Cowboys

headlines.description: Taylor Cornelius passed for 295 yards and five touchdowns in his first career start to help Oklahoma State defeat Missouri State 58-17 on Thursday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Cornelius throws 5 TDs in 1st start; Oklahoma St. rolls

video.headline: Oklahoma State RB toasts defenders on 77-yard TD run

events.name: Savannah State Tigers at UAB Blazers

headlines.description: A.J. Erdely threw for 228 yards and two touchdowns and Spencer Brown rushed for 102 yards and a score as UAB posted its first shutout since 2008 with a 52-0 victory over Savannah State in the season opener for both teams on Thursday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Elderly leads UAB to 52-0 win, 1st shutout in 10 years

events.name: Southeastern Louisiana Lions at UL Monroe Warhawks

headlines.description: Caleb Evans threw for 346 yards and two touchdowns and scored the game-winner late on the ground and FBS Louisiana-Monroe avoided an upset bid against FCS Southeastern Louisiana 34-31 Thursday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Evans leads UL-Monroe past SE Louisiana 34-31

events.name: Northwestern State Demons at Texas A&M Aggies

headlines.description: Trayveon Williams ran for 240 yards and three touchdowns in just more than two quarters as Texas A&M routed Northwestern State 59-7 in coach Jimbo Fisher's debut with the Aggies on Thursday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Williams has 240 yards rushing as A&M routs Northwestern St.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Williams breaks free for 73-yard TD) 2018/08/31

events.name: UC Davis Aggies at San Jose State Spartans

headlines.description: Jake Maier threw for 446 yards and three touchdowns and UC Davis beat San Jose State 44-38 on Thursday night for the first FCS-FBS upset of the season.
headlines.shortLinkText: UC Davis tops San Jose State 44-38 in first FCS-FBS upset
